                <a href="https://mywanderingwomb.wordpress.com/2014/12/26/royal-country-superhouse-or-why-im-currently-sitting-in-the-riga-international-airport/" target="_blank">I've lived in an isolated cabin in the woods in Latvia,</a> a trailer in the middle of Belize, <a href="https://thisisrealthisisfiction.wordpress.com/2015/07/12/rooney-the-convict-my-first-lone-day-of-hitchhiking/" target="_blank">hitchhiked with drug dealers in Washington,</a> <a href="https://thisisrealthisisfiction.wordpress.com/2014/03/01/struck-by-lightning/" target="_blank">gotten struck by lightning in India,</a> <a href="https://thisisrealthisisfiction.wordpress.com/2014/09/05/the-terrible-thing-that-didnt-happen-last-night/" target="_blank">met a drunk Irishman in the middle of the night in Chicago and leant my bike to him,</a> <a href="https://thisisrealthisisfiction.wordpress.com/2015/07/03/tour-of-temple-square-the-women-of-the-mormon-church/" target="_blank">taken a Mormon propoganda tour in Salt Lake City,</a> <a href="https://thisisrealthisisfiction.wordpress.com/2015/05/27/the-zoo-with-no-animals-exploring-detroits-abandoned-zoo/" target="_blank">explored abandoned buildings in Detroit </a>and a whole lot of other things. Here are some of my favorite stories from my blogs/travels. 
